Environment: go1.21.1 linux/amd64
Tags: with_wireguard,with_ech,with_quic,with_utls,with_reality_server,with_acme,with_clash_api,with_gvisor
CGO: disabled

ps:  实际编译的版本是 1.5.4
</details>

### 描述

acme provider使用 zerossl，dns01_challenge provider 使用 cloudflare，申请不了域名证书，报错提示：Code:6003 Message:Invalid request headers

### 重现方式

其他配置使用的acme.sh 申请的域名没问题，这里只贴tls配置部分（已脱敏）：
```json
"tls": {
                "enabled": true,
                "server_name": "www.example.com",
                "acme": {
                    "domain": ["*.example.com","www.example.com"],
                    "data_directory": "/app/config/sing-box/certs",
                    "default_server_name": "www.example.com",
                    "email": "test@gmail.com",
                    "provider": "zerossl",
                    "external_account": {
                        "key_id": "P***Q",
                        "mac_key": "TP-*****"
                    },
                    "dns01_challenge": {
                        "provider": "cloudflare",
                        "api_token": "********"
                    }
                }
            }

```
启动 singbox则报错，日志见下面

